OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather grey start with patchy
OL,6,Fdrizzle and hill fog. However, skies
OL,7,Fwill gradually brighten from the east,
OL,8,Fwith an increasingly sunny afternoon
OL,9,Fdeveloping across the region. Feeling
OL,10,Fcooler than yesterday with an easterly
OL,11,Fbreeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA fine evening with plenty of
OL,14,Flate sunshine. Some patchy low cloud
OL,15,Fand mist developing overnight,
OL,16,Fespecially over the hills, but most
OL,17,Fremaining clear. Turning chilly in the
OL,18,Fcountryside.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
