OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FAny early mist and low
OL,6,Fcloud quickly clearing leaving a fine
OL,7,Fand sunny day. Lighter winds for most
OL,8,Fallowing it to feel a little warmer.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,11,FRemaining dry, sunny and warm on
OL,12,FThursday. Sunshine increasingly hazy
OL,13,Fon Friday with a risk of showers but
OL,14,Fremaining warm and increasingly humid.
OL,15,FFresher on Saturday with further
OL,16,Fshowers possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
